BTTInlineAppleScript: -- Edit these variablesset pin to "1234"set preset to "1"set connected to do shell script "~/./.gotunl -l"considering case	if (connected contains "Connected") then		do shell script "~/./.gotunl -d \"all\""	else		do shell script "echo " & pin & " | ~/./.gotunl -c " & preset	end ifend considering

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: set response to do shell script "~/./.gotunl -l"considering case	if (response contains "Connected") then		return true	else		return false	end ifend considering
